cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the use of AI techniques for summarizing medical documents, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as it may involve the protection of sensitive medical information.
